         MACRO
         ASMVDA
AVDA     DSECT
         SPACE
***********************************************************************
*        THIS DSECT MAPS THE VDA-HEADER FOR THE ASSEMBLER VERSION OF  *
*        THE LANGUAGE-INDEPENDENT ENVIRONMENT.                        *
***********************************************************************
         SPACE
AVDACHN  DS    A                  CHAIN TO NEXT VDA
AVDALEN  DS    A                  LENGTH & SUBPOOL OF THIS VDA
         SPACE
AVDAHLEN EQU   *-AVDA             LENGTH OF THE VDA HEADER
         MEND
